apps.description:
IPTV video player for Android phone, tablet or TV.

IMPORTANT! Televizo is a video player only. Televizo does not provide any content. You must add your own playlist to watch videos or channels.

Available features:
- Support for multiple playlists;
- Support for electronic program guide (EPG);
- Catch-up support;
- Chromecast support;
- Sorting and searching;
- Parental control (playlist editor);
- Favorites;
- Audio track selection;
- Subtitles selection;
- And much more...

Terms of Service: https://televizo.net/terms-of-service.html
